CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

August 12, 2008

[Cite as 08/12/2008 Case Announcements, 2008-0hio-4056.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2007-2150. Walburn v. Dunlap.

Vinton App. No. 06CA655, 2007-Ohio-5398. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Vinton County. Upon consideration of appellees’ motion for continuance of oral argument scheduled for October 1, 2008,

It is ordered by the court that the motion is granted and the oral argument has been rescheduled for Tuesday, November 18, 2008.
